    "At this time, too, he prepared the catalog for the exhibition, <em>17th-Century Art in Europe</em>, held at the Royal Academy.": [],
    "When World War II broke out, Waterhouse was in Athens.": [],
    "He served the Military attach\u00e9 there as a cartographer, rising to the rank of major.": [],
    "In 1943 he returned to civilian status briefly to assist with the Greece embassy until the Greek civil war erupted.": [
